{
  "stem": "7832.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all these woods in this country road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then there is a jeep and a truck coming from the opposite direction with bright, bright lights.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they stopped in front of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They made-- they yelled-- they were Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were German officers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they yelled for the-- for the leader of the transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the leader went up to them and we heard him say, what-- why are you taking these Jews?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Where are you-- why are you so busy with these Jews?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The war is over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You better-- you better go and find a place to hide because the Allies are around the corner.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But these guards said, that-- they-- they-- we are going to Theresienstadt to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means, to destroy them and to the destruction camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was never in Theresienstadt so I didn't know what was going on in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when he said, [GERMAN], to destroy us, I just imagined a whole bunch of crematoriums and gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're gonna take us there and they're going to make ashes out of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's one thing Sabka and I didn't want is to become ashes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had a blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had a white blanket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a gray blanket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, Sabka, you have to throw away your blanket because it's gonna reflect in the dark.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she says, look this is the only thing that I have in my possession, and I'm not giving it up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, take my blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I gave her my blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We threw away her blanket, and I yanked her off the road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went down on the ditch, and we laid in that ditch, you know, on the side of the road until everybody passed.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
